Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto and others are out there fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:56.75,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,497)}A tool known as a Ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A tool known as a Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Old Man Giichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we all do it together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we can beat Gato and his men this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind not to fight anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The man we called a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not with us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were to fight, many lives would be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want lose something that's special to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to regret again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to regret again either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we must fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A man should live his life without regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.27,0:03:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Mommy and Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you too, Old Man Giichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I love all the people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing will be accomplished if I just cry all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Inari has grown into a fine man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you just let Inari go there by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you to fight with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man! Please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't anyone open the door to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You were too full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too ambitious for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You failed to assassinate the Mizukage and to pull off a coup d'etat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You left the service with few men under you and became a Rogue Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, your name reached Konoha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You needed to raise funds to strike back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you needed to hide from the Tracking Unit's pursuit and retaliation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that about the reason why you hired yourself out to scum like Gato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really believe I've managed\Nto survive with just my Sharingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's something I didn't copy,\Na technique of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,to enlighten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Raikiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.65,TLnote,,0,0,0,,(Lightning Cutter)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,His hand is visibly overflowing with Chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tazuna-san, the man you are trying to assassinate is the symbol of courage in this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The bridge he is building is the hope of this land!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And your ambitions will sacrifice countless lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't how a Shinobi is supposed to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have always fought for my own ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will never change!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your future is... death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you hesitating for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is remaining strong the only reason you have for staying in this worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be something other\Nthan just fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some other way for you to make others accept you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember when we met at the forest?\NDo you know what I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That you and I are much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.65,0:07:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know what i mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for dirtying your hands with my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really the only way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we had met under different circumstances we could've been friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please promise you will follow your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Him too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke also had dreams of his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. \NYou will become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The super thick fog has finally begun to clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They are facing off each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one is Kakashi Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,One moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Naruto-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.75,0:09:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Zabuza-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say my future was death?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong again, Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not to go to the bridge alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I went all over town but no one wants to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!\NYou're just a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be a child but I already know what it means to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm my father's son!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, Inari!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice but the fog is starting to lift.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is he over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.23,0:12:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the masked boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect him to jump in to save Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy, is already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great, Haku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He intends to slash me along with the boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That was really a great find I made!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in his final moment, he gave me such a perfect opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Haku, bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave the Land of Water as of tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'll return to this land someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I will rule over this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To do that, what I need isn't consolation, encouragement or empty words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What I really need is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.10,0:14:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your weapon, Zabuza-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.61,0:14:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep me by you as a mere tool\Nthat heeds your every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Haku died and you were able to move, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You just stay there and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,my battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!\NYou're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Sasuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!\NWhere is Sasuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no time to take your eyes off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That way you won't be going against your Sensei's word.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a Genjutsu, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to hold back your emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I always got perfect scores\Nat the Ninja Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I memorized hundreds of Shinobi rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All the tests were a breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Until one day, this question came up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,State Rule #25 of the Ways of the Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As always, I simply wrote down\Nthe answer without thinking twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Shinobi must never show his true feelings under any circumstances, no matter what."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"The mission always comes first."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Ninja must have the strength\Nto never to shed any tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this, how it must be for a Shinobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so unbearably painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? \NWhy can't I keep up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.22,0:19:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possibly defeat me the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.48,0:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't know what true strength means!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how things are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now both your arms have been disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even form a seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You really got it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappoint me, Zabuza.
